name: Reflection of a Nubian Queen
description:
The image, "Reflection of a Nubian Queen" created an unforgettable reflection of a Nubian Queen... a ruler, a warrior, a builder, a trader, an advisor, a mother reigning from her throne in an ancient African Kingdom on the confluences of the White Nile, and Blue Nile Rivers. Despite the darkness of the valleys, the reflection of a Nubian Queen never disappears. Thus, the naming of this image was inspired by the reflections of  Nubian Queens.

This one-of-one image was generated with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewers.
